OSP 的公开分支，逐渐关闭相关的的支持性资源，并可能停止更新有法定开源义务（GPL 等协议的代码）外的组件的源代码。 海外媒体 Android Authority 最先报道了这一情况，Google 也确认了此事。 从下周开始，所有的 Android 开发工作将仅在 Google 的内部分支进行。在一段时间后，外部分支可能将不再公开甚至彻底关闭。并且，AOSP 的持续集成/交付 (CI/CD) 工具和环境也可能关闭，甚至 Android Gerrit 也可能会关闭。 从今往后，只有 Google 内部的员工能够访问 AOSP 的内部分支，或是提交代码。Android 的开发过程将不再透明。"},"attached_info":"CkoInuyA6Pr698o2EAMaCTExNDE5NjIwNSCHspO/BjAAOJYDQAFyEzE4ODg1NzM1MjI5NDg4OTEzMzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"1023 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f4b01f0a673279704bab3c074a03559b_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1743070837.345846","card_id":"Q_1887761907844372478","target":{"id":1887761907844372500,"title":"农民工中午吃饭为什么都喜欢喝一瓶啤酒呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1887761907844372478","type":"question","created":1742857511,"answer_count":338,"follower_count":603,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3320,3574],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"难道啤酒真可以缓解疲劳吗？"},"attached_info":"CkoInuyA6Pr698o2EAMaCTExNDE1NjkxNiCnyoe/BjAAONsEQAJyEzE4ODc3NjE5MDc4NDQzNzI0Nzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"570 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0216c074288978e6b6750bf06c43772c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1743070837.346206","card_id":"Q_15663399987","target":{"id":15663399987,"title":"农村为什么要通自来水？之前井水挺甜清凉，现在的自来水总感觉有味道，通自来水是为了收费吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15663399987","type":"question","created":1742798172,"answer_count":745,"follower_count":1089,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5380],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excer